{"tid":355324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨成員被兩蝗漢毆打禁錮 何俊仁：看來跟北京無關","createTime":"2017-08-11T08:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T05:09:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07d814c664f9063c622719579dcb080778bb8b5a","tid":355324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/510476/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F510476%2F%20&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8a3dabfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F510476%2F%20&h=2d25de3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/510476/ </a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員林子健聲稱，昨日在油麻地被兩名操普通話的男子強行帶走禁錮和毆打，到今日凌晨獲釋。西九龍重案組在他報案後，接手調查。 <br />\n<br />\n民主黨前主席何俊仁對事件表示驚訝，但認為對方警告林子健的內容，與林子健被帶走毆打不成正比，以他的經驗來說，看來跟北京無關，事件的原因令人摸不著頭腦。 <br />\n<br />\n林子健在記者會之後，由民主黨議員林卓廷和支聯會秘書李卓人陪同，到瑪麗醫院急症室驗傷，要留醫治理。他向駐醫院警崗報案，並提供了資料。他解釋沒有在凌晨獲釋後即時報警，是因為太累和太緊張，先回家通知李卓人和民主黨前主席李柱銘。"},{"pid":"9dae754c83489f374db5e99107abe0455c7c0343","tid":355324,"uid":44461,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:04:01.000Z","msg":"何俊仁擺明俾人打夠唔想再俾人打"},{"pid":"2ff63f246bdee0347d941274ab7a6ba486810e16","tid":355324,"uid":35790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"大中華膠一向<br />\n反共反689<br />\n不反中央"},{"pid":"c1753d8418a792c9ae67638d9608532ab4b0d588","tid":355324,"uid":76068,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"「經驗來說」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8f3dfdaccb06d812e160f35d9ef968f00ac3f5","tid":355324,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"連登仔一鳩樣諗法"},{"pid":"2c5b7d85858939d713a41ec5dfee3a294593c47f","tid":355324,"uid":53687,"l