rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 諗起十幾年前AV仁當街比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b473212e4c067b44f11cbf458d93acfb2d163d91","tid":355324,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"都係唔跟太貼好啲"},{"pid":"3d7752b92d4e344598cb77335ec9bf457a8216be","tid":355324,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"一定又係肛派"},{"pid":"0505bbb6600d6aafc74491264c1b24cbec7c499a","tid":355324,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:53:24.000Z","msg":"原來佢都係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796fbe630ada5b32001ab8ccb5c3b646a5f8f6eb","tid":355324,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135488bfb07864eb827138bd1fa64b166c3ade40","tid":355324,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:34:37.000Z","msg":"林子健定郭子健??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fe6d65210dea20ba48e767d5cceba48e172380","tid":355324,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"今次唔會有跟車太貼<br />\n因為唔會捉到人，除非係自導自演"},{"pid":"6a91192a68a2784a6563de239ad70fa5073cc470","tid":355324,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"又一個癌上腦"}]}